headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  DUBOFSKY, ROBERT L.

lead_paragraph: DUBOFSKY--Robert L.,It is difficult to think of our world without our wonderful brother, brother-in-law, uncle and great-uncle. He will always be in our hearts. Simmy and Robert Atkins Elizabeth Atkins and Samuel Chiche Emily and Jeffrey Rosenfeld
